org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface IUnaryOperatorNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IExpressionNode, IOperatorNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UnaryOperatorAtNode, UnaryOperatorBitwiseNotNode, UnaryOperatorDeleteNode, UnaryOperatorLogicalNotNode, UnaryOperatorMinusNode, UnaryOperatorNodeBase, UnaryOperatorPlusNode, UnaryOperatorPostDecrementNode, UnaryOperatorPostfixNodeBase, UnaryOperatorPostIncrementNode, UnaryOperatorPreDecrementNode, UnaryOperatorPreIncrementNode, UnaryOperatorTypeOfNode, UnaryOperatorVoidNode

    public interface IUnaryOperatorNode
extends IOperatorNode
    An AST node representing a unary operator.

    The typical shape of this node is: 

     IUnaryOperatorNode 
   IExpressionNode <-- getOperandNode()
    For example, -a is represented as 
     IUnaryOperatorNode "-"
   IIdentifierNode "a"
